{"tid":885947,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Lenovo 抄小米推出滑蓋機 Z5 Pro!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-11-01T17:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T14:53:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"01750acac2d4dac32b898c47fe843a4abbb78dea","tid":885947,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T17:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2018-11%2F6ee84ae0-ddb0-11e8-bfed-716381d51a77&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=7ab4f8b48b548d796dc8bb630a43da8a151ad604\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2018-11%252F6ee84ae0-ddb0-11e8-bfed-716381d51a77%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D7ab4f8b48b548d796dc8bb630a43da8a151ad604&h=01ed88be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早早就預告也要推出滑蓋機的 Lenovo，如今終於在小米和榮耀之後，正式拿出了自己的產品 Z5 Pro。和小米、榮耀所用方案不同的地方在於，這款裝置選擇了所謂「六位雙螺旋」的滑蓋結構。而且除了 16MP 自拍相機、8MP 紅外線相機、紅外線燈和感應器以外，Lenovo 把聽筒也藏到了頂上推出來的部分裡面。也就是說，不管是打電話還是要實現 Z5 Pro 具備的 Dolby Atmos 聲效，你都得把滑蓋打開才行。<br />\n<br />\n不過也是得益於聽筒的移位，正面的螢幕佔比就變得更高了一些（官方自己測出來說有 95.06%）。至於螢幕本身，用的是一片 6.39 吋的 2,340 x 1,080 AMOLED 面板。Lenovo 還給它加上了 De-mura 均色技術，號稱可以解決 OLED 顯色不均勻的問題。另外光電螢幕指紋模組也是有的，可以在人臉識別以外提供另一種認證方式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2018-11%2Fbeb6d020-ddae-11e8-9bb7-5518278e0f08&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=12e8fc6d999d35537a1a912f12f1730b71a4a5d8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2018-11%252Fbeb6d020-ddae-11e8-9bb7-5518278e0f08%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D12e8fc6d999d35537a1a912f12f1730b71a4a5d8&h=84de5852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nZ5 Pro 的重量為 210g，厚度達到 9.3mm，機身上下沒有留出 3.5mm 耳機孔。和另兩家滑蓋機都是定位旗艦的做法不同，Lenovo 這款是著眼中階市場，搭載的是 Snapdragon 710 晶片。除此之外，它還配備了 6GB RAM、3,350mAh 電池和 16MP（IMX519，1.22&mu;m）+ 24MP（IMX576，0.9&mu;m）的主相機組合。預載的 ZUI 10 系統是基於 Android Oreo，繼承了 Moto 的各種手勢操作，而且有基於 NFC 的中國大陸各城市交通卡功能。<br />\n<br />\nZ5 Pro 會分為 64GB 和 128GB 兩個版本，售價分別是人民幣 1,998 和 2,298 元，即日起在大陸接受預訂。除了Z5 Pro外，Lenovo 今天還帶來了一款名為 Air 的真 &middot; 無線耳機，它支援手勢操作而且具備 IPX5 防水機能。耳機本體的 55mAh 電池可維持 3 小時的通話 / 聽歌時間，另外還有 400mAh 的充電盒作為補充，具體的價格是 298 人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/11/01/lenovo-z5-pro/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2018%2F11%2F01%2Flenovo-z5-pro%2F&d=ZBNkriTWXFMK7lyGaAQ5H%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=218c2ca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/11/01/lenovo-z5-pro/</a>"},{"pid":"5fc1812d0e8678b1d5335155af887c4af7a12d7e","tid":885947,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T17:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45214336db066b35bbf0ff5e7e61fc9e7b8bf2fd","tid":885947,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T21:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3372883ae74cad37e86ceba48b4ba8f8f1d9d2f","tid":885947,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T21:15:39.000Z","msg":"全文重點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Lenovo 今天還帶來了一款名為 Air 的真 &middot; 無線耳機，它支援手勢操作而且具備 IPX5 防水機能。耳機本體的 55mAh 電池可維持 3 小時的通話 / 聽歌時間，另外還有 400mAh 的充電盒作為補充，具體的價格是 298 人民幣。</span>"},{"pid":"85c78f3d8477b0ead7c2fb81e6be334be2d03ef9","tid":885947,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"支那廠又頂爛自己個市"},{"pid":"7437df0c3dc76038d297016c0